## General Compilation Instructions
-check
```
echo $LFS
sh is a symbolic link to bash.
/usr/bin/awk is a symbolic link to gawk.
/usr/bin/yacc is a symbolic link to bison, or to a small script that executes bison.
```
-terminal
```
lfs@debian:~$ echo $LFS
/mnt/lfs

lfs@debian:~$ ls -la /usr/bin/awk
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 21 Jun 17  2022 /usr/bin/awk -> /etc/alternatives/awk
lfs@debian:~$ ls -la /etc/alternatives/awk 
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 13 Sep 13 12:43 /etc/alternatives/awk -> /usr/bin/gawk

lfs@debian:~$ ls -la /usr/bin/yacc
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 22 Sep 19  2022 /usr/bin/yacc -> /etc/alternatives/yacc
lfs@debian:~$ ls -la /etc/alternatives/yacc
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 19 Sep 19  2022 /etc/alternatives/yacc -> /usr/bin/bison.yacc

lfs@debian:~$ ls -la /bin/sh
lrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 4 Sep 13 12:58 /bin/sh -> bash
```